<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239873>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 18. Spaniopus dissimilis Walker (♀ non type, Great Britain). 13, habitus, lateral view; 14, habitus, dorsal view; 15, head and antenna, lateral view; 16, head and antenna, frontal view; 17, fore wing; 18, scutellum and propodeum, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239873/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239877>
    dc:description "FIGURES 40 – 45. Spaniopus spp. 40 – 42. Spaniopus dissimilis Walker (♂ lectotype). 40, habitus, dorsal view; 41, head and antenna, dorsal view; 42, mid tibia, lateral view. 43 – 45. Spaniopus monospilus (Thomson) (♂ lectotype). 43, antenna; 44, mid tibia, lateral view; 45, head, frontal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239877/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

